    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing to express my sadness and disappointment regarding the recent decision on demolishing of the Old Dutch Hospital building situated in Peta area to build a new shopping complex. I have been living in this area since I was born and probably explains why I have an emotional attachment to this monument building.",
        "The Dutch Hospital is one of a historical building which built during the Dutch era. It has Dutch architectural influence and adds incredible aesthetic value to the city. Furthermore, it was observed that many tourists visit this place as a result of famous architecture. The visitors can have a sense of the culture during the past. Demolishing such valuable property is not the right decision.",
        "Most of the local guides, shops and local restaurants around the area are benefiting because of great attraction. Furthermore, the city is famous among the tourists, mainly because of the historical values the building carrying.",
        "I appreciate if you could reconsider this decision, and I would like to see a positive outcome.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Nethandun Wijethilaka"
